{
  "stem": "9963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On that mountain, I-- one time, where I'd almost fall down also, because I hit myself right here with a pick-axe, you know, what we digged out the stones-- but went in here, and came out there, you know, and I'd-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --but when that happened-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when that happened, I'd felt very, very bad pain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just grabbed myself at the soles not to fall down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I hardly could go ahead, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- that-- where I had somebody had to help you to go down and to go to a-- back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And over there, they-- we didn't had any doctors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he give me the three days to recuperate-- not to go back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I couldn't walk on the leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he give me three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the three days, I took a permission to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I came home, and that didn't healed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Matter of fact, it got worse, because I didn't have any vitamins in me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have anything, you know, to-- any medication what that-- to make it heal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that got worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as that got worse, I didn't want to go-- I-- go back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I ran away from the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I-- as I didn't went back, the police start looking for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I was at the farmer's, you know, I know farmers from before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I went to them, and I ask them to keep me over there and to give me to eat, only to eat, you know, and I would do all kind of work for them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They needed tailoring, you know, like fixing up for children and for themselves and others.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
